data.title: Fox Surf Presents | 12th annual Ian Walsh Menehune Mayhem
data.description:
The 12th annual Ian Walsh Menehune Mayhem was the biggest and best year yet. Over 150 kids from all over Hawaii competed at Ho’okipa Beach on Sat April 4th. This event celebrates Ian’s passion for the ocean as well as gives a carnival atmosphere for the kids to keep the fun going all day long. Check out this video and see how the Ian and Island of Maui give back to the next generation of surfers.
